ctu.nengoros.comm.nodeFactory.demo.turtle

Class RuNativeCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • ctu.nengoros.comm.nodeFactory.demo.turtle.RuNativeCode

  • public class RuNativeCode
extends java.lang.Object
    This is old demo, shows how to launch external process.. Here is the demo how we are able to launch arbitrary native application on Unix platform. Note that this demo uses installation of ROS fuerte and compiled source code of turtlesim (which is also (a copied) part of ROS installation). So this demo will work correctly only on Unix system with ROS installed.
